							<h3><a href="#">About PVKKIT II Shift Diploma</a></h3>
						<p >PVKKIT, the premier promoter of quality education in Andhra Pradesh for the last 10 years, is the brain child of Dr. Palle Raghunatha Reddy garu. Sprouting in the garden of Sri Balaji Educational Society, PVKKIT rose to the level of becoming the bench-mark for quality engineering education.</p>
						<p >PVKKIT made its entry into the technical education arena in 2008 with the approval of AICTE and is affiliated to JNTUA with an intake of 240 seats primarily in 4 U.G courses in Engineering & Technology.</p>
						<p >The college is situated amidst lush and luxurious greenery in a sprawling 26 acres land. The College has spacious, well ventilated, well equipped, and well furnished Laboratories, Workshops, E - Class Rooms, Drawing Halls, Hostels and a well stocked Central Library with about 40,000+ volumes of books with digital access to all volumes and books in Library on Android and iOS platforms. In the present academic year an additional block was built to accommodate the Diploma and MBA courses.</p>
						<p >Beginning with a modest intake of 240 students in 5 branches in 2008, the college has grown in size and infrastructure to admit 480 students in 5 branches of B.Tech right now. To facilitate the higher educational needs of Under Graduates, the college has started M.Tech Courses in 5 specializations, and offers MBA course.<br />
 <br />Apart from Graduate and Under Graduate courses, the college is also running 2nd shift diploma course in Civil, ECE, EEE and Mechanical branches from the academic year 2013-14.<br />
<br />To further academic excellence among students, we have Student Chapters for each branch of engineering.  They conduct seminars and quizzes on technical topics and organize technical and industrial visits. They also provide exposure to the students on current technologies by arranging lectures of eminent persons from Academia and industry. 
</p>
